
You immediately run up the stairs into the commons.
Finally at the first floor, you try the front doors, but to no avail. 
You tried the other doors as well, but it was no use. You decide to look around you.
There is the reception’s desk near the entrance.
The Avanti market is locked.
There are clothes for sale behind a locked gate.
The rest of the commons is filled with tables and chairs, except the imaging bar.
There are three doors, the front door, the side door, and the back door.